00:01:21.480 --> 00:01:24.700
A blood test is the only way to detect if you have it.

00:01:24.700 --> 00:01:27.020
Dietary changes, regular exercise,

00:01:27.020 --> 00:01:30.600
and sometimes medication can help reduce high cholesterol.

00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:32.340
If you have high cholesterol,

00:01:32.340 --> 00:01:34.580
your doctor may prescribe statins.

00:01:34.580 --> 00:01:36.580
Statins are a class of drugs that

00:01:36.580 --> 00:01:38.740
help lower cholesterol levels in the blood.

00:01:38.740 --> 00:01:42.260
Statins work by blocking the production of LDL,

00:01:42.260 --> 00:01:46.020
resulting in reduced LDL cholesterol levels in the blood.
